com.asm.analysis

Class CodeIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.asm.analysis.CodeIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<CodeIterator.CodePart>

    public class CodeIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<CodeIterator.CodePart>
    Very simple code analysis utility. This implements Iterator, and next() returns the part of code. CodePart includes three things: text, index, type. This separate the code, like " to ", // to \n, the variable name(a-z, A-Z, ..). This also separate all the operators, such as ; , . " = / ( ... The type indicates what it is, like text(surrounded with ""/''/...), comment (/* ... *\/, // ... \n), normal(plain, such as int, abc, class, ArrayList).
